Paper: hep-th/9211024

Date: 1992-11-04

Title: Discretization of the Superparticle Path Integral

Authors: J. Grundberg, U. Lindstrom and H. Nordstrom

Comments: 10 pages

Journal-ref: Mod. Phys. Lett. A8 (1993) 1323-1330

Requiring that the path integral has the global symmetries of the classicalaction and obeys the natural composition property of path integrals, and alsothat the discretized action has the correct naive continuum limit, we find aviable discretization of the (D=3,N=2) superparticle action.